  "",
  "“My sister!”",
  "beams Proserpina, nudging Effie forward.",
  "",
  "“Oh, it was a privilege to dress them for Panem,” says Effie modestly.",
  "",
  "Drusilla’s face twists through a range of expressions — confusion, relief, admiration, with bitterness ultimately winning.",
  "“These cannot be credited to Magno.",
  "You.”",
