  "",
  "A flutter of chiffon at my elbow alerts me to the arrival of all four District 6 doves, who shimmer in their iridescent gray finery.",
  "Beetee moves down to a meatball pyramid without further clarifications, a good-bye, or a good luck.",
  "",
  "Wellie whispers, “Ampert says, when we get to the arena, we’re supposed to band together as soon as possible.”",
  "",
  "Is that by design?",
